Step by step to boot the application:
We used a local model to process the documents for the embedding
We also used UV, a python project manager for better handling of our project
use:
uv run basic_ui.py
to run the application

UV instalation guide:

Tools used:
Langchain library
Copilot for most of the code generation and assistent/agent support
Gemini was also used a few times
Llama and local AI models
SQLite for database
ChromaDB to set up the embedding vector database
Using UV to handle dependencies